正常<br />\n計比例，當你咩都唔識你見東亞人正常都估咗中文先啦<br />\n好似香港人咪又係見白鬼又當母語係英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知好正常，唔怪佢。<br />\n但作為香港人善意話反比佢哋聽粵語嘅存在都應該呀。"},{"pid":"4d56d6fb19c6837d6f0403907a7734d84189df32","tid":318573,"uid":2106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係 普遍都唔會識分<br />\n唔好用香港人身份打飛機啦<br />\n同埋出去旅行 好多香港人係最仆街個堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正解"},{"pid":"a24d7ee6c81c5109df845db0bd3b28d918576013","tid":318573,"uid":33004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係 普遍都唔會識分<br />\n唔好用香港人身份打飛機啦<br />\n同埋出去旅行 好多香港人係最仆街個堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正解</blockquote><br />\n等俾班港豬話你五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f209537f2db188266ff92c336e9cbe4028cae84","tid":318573,"uid":117556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係 普遍都唔會識分<br />\n唔好用香港人身份打飛機啦<br />\n同埋出去旅行 好多香港人係最仆街個堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正解</blockquote><br />\n等俾班港豬話你五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係黑社會 唔係港豬"},{"pid":"9f3bcd36283061bb995c2bd69a024b0e1eac3f9a","tid":318573,"uid":51200,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:56:25.000Z","msg":"一有人同我講ni hao，<br />\n我就會同返佢講，<br />\nI come from Hong Kong .We speak in Cantonese.<br />\n通常佢地會say返句sorry.<br />\n<br />\n有一次個鬼佬用普通話問我：你是中國人嗎？<br />\n我即刻講返上面嗰句。<br />\n點知佢死唔斷氣講,but you still understand what I was saying right? I actually live in China<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就同返佢講，Just a little bit，because we are near China. <br />\nBut we Hongkongese will only speak in Cantonese.<br />\nHong Kong is Hong Kong. China is China.<br />\n個鬼佬先say sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360c9a77464f33a2c4a42051cd2eca2e8df0b6ca","tid":318573,"uid":683,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T19:00:27.000Z","msg":"人在外國，打算黎緊會經A國去B國，B國比特區護照免簽，但A國無免簽，於是要搞A國過程簽證，咁我打電話過去問，對話如下：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：A國簽證官<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你好，我黎緊會經A去B，想搞Transit visa<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：好呀，你有無B國visa？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：無呀，我護照有得免簽證入B國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你拎邊個國家護照？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：HKSAR<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：哦&hellip;&hellip;香港呀，中國護照無B國免簽架喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：香港護照同中國護照唔同架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：點解會唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我問下同事先<br />\n<br />\n十分鐘後<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：成間大使館都無人都無人聽過香港護照有咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：屌你真係唔撚同架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我地就聽都未聽過既，一係你申請我地transit visa個陣帶埋B國官方既證明過黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果我要去B國大使館叫佢出封證明信比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97746ebf12789e23d3be5c61a9bb223df35851dc","tid":318573,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T19:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一有人同我講ni hao，<br />\n我就會同返佢講，<br />\nI come from Hong Kong .We speak in Cantonese.<br />\n通常佢地會say返句sorry.<br />\n<br />\n有一次個鬼佬用普通話問我：你是中國人嗎？<br />\n我即刻講返上面嗰句。<br />\n點知佢死唔斷氣講,but you still understand what I was saying right? I actually live in China<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就同返佢講，Just a little bit，because we are near China. <br />\nBut we Hongkongese will only speak in Cantonese.<br />\nHong Kong is Hong Kong. China is China.<br />\n個鬼佬先say sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲鬼只係純真地覺得想用試下用人地嘅語言，以示畀人睇自己好叻<br />\n但係佢地唔知香港人好憎支那同蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62a6d0f8e54d76a8d481c170411ad505e681b2d","tid":318573,"uid":126247,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T19:16:54.000Z","msg":"你見到白人咪又係假定人地識講英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74fe0fb28fc49c70bf63554d6be52af15cec918","tid":318573,"uid":50196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201